{
  "stem": "17135.6",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 394.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was an organization.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was the Vice President.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we, at that time, all we wanted, the people to testify.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Although they're-- they're-- there was no videotapes available, it was in the '60s, in the early-- no, in the '50s.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when I came here I got involved very, very intimately in Holocaust causes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1960.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In January, 1960.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked in the garment industry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I've went to school at the same time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but I mean Jew-- in--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, oh, oh, oh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got involved in the 1939 Club and got very active, involved.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to go-- years ago, I used to go to-- to-- to high schools and-- and-- and-- and tell about the holocaust.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And especially, I told you, after I was involved in-- in-- in testifying, I learned more.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I used to teach people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I got involved in-- in-- in-- also in-- in-- in the Hebrew University and [INAUDIBLE] University, Tel Aviv University.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I got involved in the Federation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The '39 Club is a fraternal organization of survivors of the Holocaust, primarily from Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there are also some German Jews and a few Hungarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Especially if they're married to Polish Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it started with Polish Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now they-- they're in their late-- they started in '51 or something like this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And later they realized that it-- it's not only Polish Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took anybody that was a survivor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they did a-- they did a very good job in-- in educating the public, in supporting a lot of causes in Israel.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were the first organization that established a chair for the study of the Holocaust at a public university.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know that the UCLA has a Chair.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
